## Limitations

This report is based on a limited selection of sources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was restricted to articles available online, which may exclude valuable insights from print publications or less accessible resources. Additionally, the report focuses primarily on the educational benefits of teaching Black history, potentially overlooking other societal or cultural implications. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.